title: Fix TypeScript build errors in auth and integrations routes
description: Backend TypeScript build was failing with 6 errors. Fixed duplicate property 'user' in auth.ts registration response and duplicate/undefined schema exports in integrations.ts.
fixes: Fixed object property override in auth.ts line 110 - moved user object after spread operator
Removed duplicate createWebhookSchema export from integrations.ts line 89
Removed duplicate createApiKeySchema export (already exported on line 16)
result: TypeScript build now passes with 0 errors (was 6 errors)
